    Keepin SDK
    Add service id in AndroidManifest.xml
    Initializing SDK
    try { KeepinSDK sdk = new KeepinSDK(getContext()); } catch (NotInstalledKeepinException e) { // goto google play store startAcitivity(getActivity(), e.getIntent()); }
